## ⏱️ Complexity Analysis

Let `n` be the number of intervals.

### Time Complexity

* Sorting: **O(n log n)**
* Single traversal: **O(n)**

Overall:

```text id="fw66pr"
O(n log n)
```

### Space Complexity

```text id="3kmthx"
O(1)
```

Ignoring the space used internally by the sorting algorithm.

